    <item>
      <title>习近平推出大规模刺激计划 旨在结束中国经济放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/xi-s-big-stimulus-week-aims-to-draw-a-line-under-china-slowdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[几个月来，尽管股市下跌、物价下跌、中国各地的不满情绪不断增长，但国家主席习近平似乎并未因经济增长放缓而感到不安。本周，他表明自己不愿再忍受任何痛苦。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/xi-s-big-stimulus-week-aims-to-draw-a-line-under-china-slowdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 09:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>CD&R 将债务融资股权期权排除在赛诺菲最终竞标之外</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/cd-r-excludes-debt-funded-equity-option-from-final-sanofi-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Clayton Dubilier &amp; Rice 提出的条件是，银行必须承担超过 10 亿欧元（11 亿美元）的债务，为竞购赛诺菲消费者健康部门提供部分股权检查资金，但这笔贷款并未出现在最终提交给这家制药公司的方案中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/cd-r-excludes-debt-funded-equity-option-from-final-sanofi-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 09:13:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国取消电网连接队列中部分停滞的“僵尸”项目</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/uk-axes-10gw-of-zombie-projects-in-grid-connections-queue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国电网运营商已砍掉了 10 千兆瓦的停滞“僵尸”能源项目，从而切断了阻碍该国清洁能源转型关键基础设施建设的进程。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/uk-axes-10gw-of-zombie-projects-in-grid-connections-queue</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 08:58:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>默多克旗下 REA 第四次提出英国众议院选址提案 Rightmove</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/murdoch-s-rea-makes-fourth-proposal-for-uk-house-site-rightmove</link>
      <description><![CDATA[REA Group Ltd. 在不到一个月的时间内第四次向 Rightmove Plc 提出收购要约，对这家英国房地产门户网站的估值约为 62 亿英镑（87 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/murdoch-s-rea-makes-fourth-proposal-for-uk-house-site-rightmove</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 08:52:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>桑坦德银行与 DE Shaw 合作对冲与法国农业信贷银行的合资企业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/santander-turns-to-de-shaw-to-hedge-venture-with-credit-agricole</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，西班牙桑坦德银行对其在与法国农业信贷银行成立的资产服务合资企业中的股权进行了对冲，以减轻监管负担。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/santander-turns-to-de-shaw-to-hedge-venture-with-credit-agricole</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 08:50:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲债券价格飙升，欧洲央行 10 月降息可能性增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/european-bonds-surge-with-ecb-cut-in-october-increasingly-likely</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲债券价格周五上涨，延续一周涨势，这使得十月份降息的可能性大大增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/european-bonds-surge-with-ecb-cut-in-october-increasingly-likely</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 08:40:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受制裁的亿万富翁在与老朋友争夺 PhosAgro 股份时获胜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/sanctioned-billionaire-wins-fight-with-old-friend-over-phosagro-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受到制裁的俄罗斯亿万富翁安德烈·古里耶夫 (Andrey Guryev) 在与一位老朋友的法庭斗争中获胜，这位老朋友声称古里耶夫违背了在伦敦一家酒吧喝啤酒时做出的承诺，即分享其在全球最大化肥生产商之一的股份。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/sanctioned-billionaire-wins-fight-with-old-friend-over-phosagro-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 08:08:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国股市爆发数年来最大买入狂潮 交易所应接不暇</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/china-stocks-climb-as-fiscal-stimulus-bets-woo-more-buyers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国股市创下 2008 年以来最大单周涨幅，上海证券交易所交易火爆，凸显出习近平政府加大经济刺激措施后投资者情绪发生剧烈转变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/china-stocks-climb-as-fiscal-stimulus-bets-woo-more-buyers</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 02:02:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>供应增加前景导致油价周线大幅下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-27</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价在连续两天大幅下跌后企稳，由于石油输出国组织 (OPEC) 成员国沙特阿拉伯和利比亚有望增加供应，油价仍将出现本周大幅下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-27</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 23:25:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>PCE 数据公布前股市涨势暂停；日元上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周结束时，股市涨跌互现，美国和欧洲基准指数在市场对央行宽松政策和中国刺激措施的乐观情绪下创下新高。日本大选结果公布后，日元转而上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 22:40:32 GMT</pubDate>
